<description><![CDATA[This recipe is a great recipe for anyone wanting to improve their sense of tasting, balancing and adjusting flavours. The final step of tasting and adjusting the salt, pepper, chili, lemon and olive oil and teasing out the flavours of the herbs and tomato is a great exercise in learning to season.

